parameters.name: MaxResults
parameters.description: The number of entries per page. Valid values: 10 to 100. Default value: 50.

parameters.name: Name
parameters.description: The name of the parameter. **You can enter a keyword to query parameter names in fuzzy match mode.

parameters.name: NextToken
parameters.description: The token that is used to retrieve the next page of results.

parameters.name: Path
parameters.description: The path of the parameter. For example, if the name of a parameter is /path/path1/Myparameter, the path of the parameter is /path/path1/.

parameters.name: Recursive
parameters.description: Specifies whether to query parameters from all levels of directories in the specified path. Default value: false.

parameters.name: ResourceGroupId
parameters.description: The ID of the resource group.

parameters.name: SortField
parameters.description:
The field used to sort the query results. Valid values:

*   Name
*   CreatedDate

parameters.name: SortOrder
parameters.description:
The order in which the entries are sorted. Valid values:

*   Ascending
*   Descending (Default)
